      class="underline"
      href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL8bLS57CI8i2idWqYbsvu9IOwjTGqReaa"
      >link to my playlist on YouTube</a
    >.</p>  
    <p>If you'd like me to come speak at your conference, please <a href="/contact">fill out this form</a>.</p>
